SMELL: The bathroom structure is located in the nursing room, but the bathroom exhaust fan has been disabled, making the whole room very smelly. If this exhaust fan operates, the amount of outside air coming in will be the stinging air from the parking lot on the ground floor that rushes into the rooms on the upper floors due to the skylight design connecting directly from the parking area. As long as the ground floor is still used to park cars, this problem will still exist even if there is a restriction on starting the car engine when entering and exiting the parking area. Or solve it by opening the outside ventilation windows for each room and taking care of the bathroom exhaust system more often. Need to pay more attention to hygiene in the nursing room. 4. POST-BIRTH CARE: Cleaning for women after giving birth every day is very necessary, but most women do not dare to use this service a second time because it is very painful. NOISE: The issue of visitation is not strictly enforced, allowing many relatives to bring children to stay with them, it is like a kindergarten for all ages so it is extremely noisy.
